name biblatex-gb7714-2015
category Package
revision 78680
shortdesc A BibLaTeX implementation of the GB/T 7714 series bibliography styles for Chinese users
longdesc This package provides the implementation of bibliography styles
longdesc for the GB/T 7714 series standards, such as GB/T 7714-1987,
longdesc GB/T 7714-2005, GB/T 7714-2015, GB/T 7714-2025. The package
longdesc also provides several liberal arts bibliography styles, such as
longdesc chinese-erj, chinese-css, chinese-jmw, and so on. These styles
longdesc can be used simply by loading BibLaTeX with the appropriate
longdesc option.
